{{Infobox video game |title=Glimmerati |image= |developer = [[Bugbear Entertainment]] |publisher = [[Nokia]] |designer = |engine = |released={{vgrelease|EU|July 7, 2005|NA|August 16, 2005}} |genre = [[Racing]] |modes = [[Single player]], [[Multiplayer]], [[N-Gage Arena]] |platforms=[[N-Gage (device)|N-Gage]] }}
'''''Glimmerati''''' is a 2005 racing video game developed by [[Bugbear Entertainment]] and published by [[Nokia]] for the Nokia [[N-Gage (device)|N-Gage]].
==Story== In the game's story, the player is a wealthy heir who meets with another wealthy man one day, and he admires the player's skill in driving. He invites the player to compete with Club Glimmerati, an exclusive gathering of famous and rich people who race in the public streets for fun.
